snippet.title: "A Roof Over Your Shed" (part1)... Using Similar Triangles (TrigA2)
snippet.description: Situational Math video for right angle trigonometry: Similar triangles are used to compare the slope of a shed roof to standard roof pitches as "something in twelve". The connection between the slope or pitch and the tangent ratio is also introduced.
